OL,5, Inequalities between children in the   
OL,6, north of England compared to those in  
OL,7, the rest of the country have got worse 
OL,8, during the pandemic, a report says.    
OL,10,FNearly all children have suffered, but 
OL,11,Fresearchers said those in the North    
OL,12,FEast, North West and Yorkshire and the 
OL,13,FHumber had poorer educational outcomes.
OL,15,FThe Child of the North report warned   
OL,16,Fthe inequalities would cost billions   
OL,17,Fand increase poverty in the future.    
OL,19,FThe government said it was supporting  
OL,20,Fpupils to make up for lost learning.   
